Description: Envoy configuration management tool - manage complex Envoy configs using simple
 YAML fragments
 envoyctl is a configuration management and deployment tool for Envoy Proxy. It
 lets you manage complex Envoy configurations using small, focused YAML
 fragments, validates the generated configuration using Envoy itself, and safely
 applies changes via systemd or Docker.

